UPDATE db_script_string SET content_loc5='你不是真的以為我會再和你做生意吧?有時候，要回收利潤的方法就是知道何時該切斷你的盈虧。' WHERE entry=2000005833; /* content: You didn\'t really think I\'d do business with you again, did you? Sometimes, the best way to return to profitability is to know when to cut your losses. */
UPDATE db_script_string SET content_loc5='我的佩劍阿契厄斯伴隨了我一生，但是現在我的靈魂已經脫離了痛苦，我已經不再需要它了。' WHERE entry=2000005834; /* content: My sword Archeus served me well in life, but as at last my spirit may pass from the unhappy existence, I need it no longer. */
